components.value: Rabaan has his back turned, perfect for a surprise attack. With the
weight of every loved one that perished when their home was destroyed,
Nerala feels the anger and the guilt building up inside her.
Finally, Nerala snaps back and clears her mind, taking the opportunity to slash
Rabaan on the forearm with a poisonous blade. Rabaan, unknowingly, laughs again.
Rabban - "Your attacks are useless against me you fool. now die
you waste of flesh"  killing Nerala and throwing her body aside.
At the same time, he starts coughing and falls to his knees.His eyes open widely,
fear flashing through them for the first time in his life.
Rabban - No... is not possible... No! What have you done to me!
You are nothing more than insects!!!
In a furious rage Nerala lunges forward, ignoring Zhib’s advice.
Rabaan turns and catches her before the attack lands and laughs at the trio.
